<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PetConnection</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        main {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-4 mt-4">
        <h1>Welcome to PetConnect</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="intro" class="mb-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <img src="/assets/found-dog.jpg" alt="Header Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="text-center">About PetConnect</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">Welcome to PetConnect, your ultimate destination for reuniting lost pets with their loving owners through the power of pictures...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="mission" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-center">At PetConnect, our mission is to bring solace to pet owners in times of distress by reuniting them with their lost pets...</p>
        </section>

        <section id="how-it-began" class="mb-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <img src="/assets/dog-puppy.jpg" alt="Dog Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="text-center">How It All Began</h2>
                    <p>The story of PetConnect started with a simple idea, to use the ever-present cameras around us to help lost pets find their way back home...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="how-we-work" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">How We Work</h2>
            <p class="text-center">PetConnect is a platform where anyone can contribute to the cause of reuniting lost pets with their owners...</p>
        </section>

        <section id="our-community" class="mb-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <img src="/assets/cat.jpg" alt="Cat Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="text-center">Our Community</h2>
                    <p>At the heart of PetConnect is our compassionate and dedicated community of pet lovers, volunteers, and everyday heroes...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="privacy-safety" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Privacy and Safety</h2>
            <p class="text-center">PetConnect is committed to the privacy and safety of all its users.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
